    "description": "You have one goal - help all the HopHops escape by navigating them to hot air balloons! Do this before the Foxes catch them, otherwise it's game over!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/7237bf115acf40b798a2ff026357563d.poster.avif?t=1725178791\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/7237bf115acf40b798a2ff026357563d.webm?t=1725178791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/7237bf115acf40b798a2ff026357563d.mp4?t=1725178791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play through many puzzle sets, create your own puzzles, and then share or play puzzles online!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/b6e6dec2c576d89f2f03c64e590e59d3.avif?t=1725178791\" width=617 height=113 /></span><br><br>Get ready to give your brain a workout with laid-back puzzles based around designing the flow of HopHops around the game board.<br><br>The rules are simple:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> HopHops and Foxes will always move forward until they hit a wall.<br></li><li> If they hit a wall, they will turn right until they can continue walking forward.<br></li><li> You must place arrows to change their direction, directing the HopHops out of harm's way and towards their escape!</li></ul><br>There are many different puzzle sets to try, each with its own theme and varying difficulties. You can also look forward to regular and <strong>free updates</strong> with fresh content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/34575d4c8e10e5357fe71e824f43c409.avif?t=1725178791\" width=617 height=113 /></span><br><br>Solving puzzles is fun - but when you're done solving, you may want to try your hand at creating! <br><br>HopHop Fox lets you hop into the driver's seat and begin creating your own puzzles. Use the puzzle creator to start building your own brain-teasers and share them with your friends and the world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019740/extras/e479041841aac88794d4fc1066293daa.avif?t=1725178791\" width=617 height=113 /></span><br><br>Waiting for the release of new puzzle sets or itching to see how others handle your puzzle creations? <br><br>With the Online mode, you can select 3 of your puzzles to represent you online and see how many other plays succeed or fail in solving them. You can also attempt to solve puzzles representing other players - good luck!",
